Package io.github.jornegitgud.galaxyquest

Class GalaxySettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jornegitgud.galaxyquest.GalaxySettings
  • public class GalaxySettings
extends java.lang.Object
    this is the class that holds all the settings for the galaxy. this class is also responsible for changing these settings.

      • GalaxySettings

        public GalaxySettings()

      • GalaxySettings

        public GalaxySettings​(int width,
                      int height,
                      int planetCount,
                      int pirateCount,
                      java.lang.Boolean settingsFrozen,
                      int meteoriteCount)
        Constructor to build a custom galaxy.
        Parameters:
        width - sets the width of the galaxy but, checks if it is within the min and max width limits of the galaxy first
        height - sets the height of the galaxy but, checks if it is within the min and max height limits of the galaxy first
        planetCount - sets the planetCount of the galaxy but, checks if the galaxy wont be to populated first
        pirateCount - sets the pirateCount of the galaxy but, checks if the galaxy wont be to populated first
        settingsFrozen - freezes the galaxy settings so the numbers cant be edited in the middle of a game.
        meteoriteCount - sets the meteoriteCount of the galaxy but, checks if the galaxy wont be to populated first
